The paper deals with a multiuser MIMO system with downlink transmission, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI) concepts. The use of precoding and spreading techniques also falls under the category of signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the use of space-time block codes (cs.MM) and their encoding/decoding using differential modulation. Finally, the paper proposes low complexity transceivers, which can be considered as a communication and networking topic (cs.COM).
